text: Alfonso Bobadilla (born 19 November 1951) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
